<plot>Prominent jazz musicians of the 1940's get together for a rare filming of a jam session. 'Marie Bryant' (qv) has a vocal, and dancer 'Archie Savage' (qv) does the jitterbug. It is notable that for several cast members, this is their only known appearance in a theatrical film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?273464</url></doc>
